Job Title: DataStage Developer
Job Location: ALBANY NY 12210
Job Expected Duration: 6 + Months

Job Requirement: 
At least five (5) years working on large scale Data Mart / Data Warehouse projects; 
At least seven (5) years of experience in DataStage ETL development while utilizing best-practice; 
At least five (5) years of experience designing and implementing ETL solutions with IBM DataStage in a UNIX / Linux environment including its installation, configuration and performance tuning; 
At least four (4) years of experience with database programming in a large enterprise environments; 
At least three (3) years in source data analysis defining data granularity, data element mapping, data warehouse design and data aggregation; 
At least three (3) years of experience with data conversions; and 
At least two (2) years of experience in Data Quality & Data Governance. 
Experience with Medicaid, HIX or Health data is a plus


Thanks,
Matheen Ahmed
IT Recruiter
